title: Abbys Ultimate Dance Competition S02E10
description:
Episode: 10
Divas in the House
Original Airdate: November 5, 2013 It's "Diva" week and our dancers and their moms are happy to oblige. In a fierce dance version of kickball where the kids get to choose their dance styles one-by-one, leaving one unlucky dancer with the style no one else wanted. Some of the dancers choose wisely, but others find themselves on the wrong side of the biggest diva in the house--Abby Lee Miller, of course.
